.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n到我有工返，都遇過類似既組織，又係幫小朋友既，有次say no，因為份糧只係啱啱好夠生活，佢都用過道德勒索話「咁你係咪唔關心啲有需要既小朋友啦？」，但語氣冇咁強同冇黑面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。有次遇返佢地就捐左少少。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T09:00:38.000Z","msg":"緊係大大聲答 ： 係，關鳩我事咩"},{"pid":"d0dbc4d619da0172c7a1b6a378b0088b9895376c","tid":2331523,"uid":94266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9030502e67c5a82d97ce54e924958e31e63e365c","tid":2331523,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T08:43:03.000Z","msg":"其實你知唔知喺街就叫人捐錢嗰啲都係收佣跑數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T09:08:29.000Z","msg":"真係唔知。以前年少無知，依家見到佢地都唔會停低腳步。"},{"pid":"f51a6551a772fcbefd9cc6180ace5702bcd3b99f","tid":2331523,"uid":70417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T09:13:02.000Z","msg":"試過同啲sales講: 係人都知啲細路慘啦，咁你都要話我知你有幾%錢係行政費幾%錢真係幫人先得嫁，唔係點說服人呀<br />\n然後啲sales講左句手頭上冇數據，然後繼續講啲細路幾慘<br />\n神經病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d68c60f080f2d0a9a7971c58cc1a9ab808df76e8","tid":2331523,"uid":47374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T09:20:47.000Z","msg":"有日趕返工好聲好氣拒絕，<br />\n條友都chur足我兩條街，<br />\n最後話：唔係我生，關我撚事"},{"pid":"7f90f92587bc7e40ecbcaccb09ed551394363c3a","tid":2331523,"uid":20262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T09:24:06.000Z","msg":"做慈善事業嘅人多數仆街"},{"pid":"1715f830445bf5ed3ec0b9b4430dfbc1781c9000","tid":2331523,"uid":94266,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"734c571812f08674d1cab5747cb1329a73d17bc3","tid":2331523,"uid":37525,"like":2,"dislike":9,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T02:40:02.000Z","msg":"個問題應該係唔諗住捐<br />\n唔好叫人過嚟sell<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nsell完得個吉 係人都屌柒你<br />\n浪費大家時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkg